# Inventory Management API

A containerized Inventory Management REST API built with Flask, PostgreSQL, and Podman Compose.

## Technologies

- Flask
- PostgreSQL
- Podman
- Podman Compose
- Python
- psycopg2

## Features

- List products
- Get a product by ID
- Create a product
- Update a product
- Delete a product

## Run

```bash
podman compose up --build -d
```

API:

```
http://localhost:5000
```

### Endpoints

GET /products

GET /products/{id}

POST /products

PUT /products/{id}

DELETE /products/{id}